<template>
  <v-card style="width" sv-for="item in contacts" :key="item.job_id">
    <v-card-title prepend-inner-icon="mdi-account">{{
      item.u_name
    }}</v-card-title>
  </v-card>
</template>
<script setup>
import { useStore } from "vuex";
import { computed, onMounted } from "vue";
const store = useStore();
const contacts = computed(() => {
  return store.state.contractor.contacts;
});
onMounted(() => {
  store.dispatch("triggerSetContacts");
});
</script>
<style scoped></style>
